    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Completly custom android dialog]]></title>
    <link href="http://schibsted-tech-polska.github.io/blog/blog/2014/12/03/completly-custom-android-dialog/"/>
    <updated>2014-12-03T10:25:00+01:00</updated>
